data_table.description: ubject ID, ethnicity, gender, case or control of participant, neoplasm behavior, age at entry into cohort, age at diagnosis, age at blood draw, estrogen receptor status, and family history of breast cancer of participants with or without breast cancer and involved in the "GWAS in African Americans, Latinos and Japanese" project.

variable.name: STATUS
variable.description: Case or control status of participant

variable.name: BEHAVIOR
variable.comment: This variable will be missing for control subjects

variable.name: AGE_CAT
variable.description: Age at entry into cohort (baseline) in 5 year intervals
variable.comment: Age at entry to cohort was used to match cases and controls

variable.name: AGEDX_CAT
variable.description: Age at diagnosis for cancer cases

variable.name: AGECO_CAT
variable.description: Age at blood draw for controls

variable.name: FH_BCA
variable.description: Family history of breast cancer (sister or mother) reported at baseline
